exercises.name: Push-ups
exercises.description: Do push-ups with your hands on the ground

exercises.name: Sit-ups
exercises.description: Lie down and sit up, touching your toes

exercises.name: Squats
exercises.description: Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and squat down

exercises.name: Lunges
exercises.description: Step forward with one leg and bend the knee until the thigh is parallel to the ground

exercises.name: Plank
exercises.description: Hold your body in a straight line from head to toe, supported by your forearms and toes

exercises.name: Bicep Curl
exercises.description: Curl the dumbbell towards your shoulder

exercises.name: Tricep Pushdown
exercises.description: Stand facing a cable machine with a rope or bar attached. Grasp the rope or bar with an overhand grip and position your elbows at your sides. Keeping your upper arms stationary, extend the rope or bar down by contracting your triceps, then slowly return to the starting position.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Fly
exercises.description: Extend your arms out to the side and bring them back together

exercises.name: Bulgarian Split Squat
exercises.description: Hold the barbell on your shoulders and squat down

exercises.name: Pull-up
exercises.description: Hang from a bar with your palms facing away from your body and pull yourself up until your chin is over the bar

exercises.name: Deadlift
exercises.description: Lift the barbell off the ground and stand up straight
